properties.SHORT_DESCRIPTION:
Fish sampling will be conducted to:
1.Determine species assemblage and upstream limits of distribution for fish species in Fitzsimmons Creek;
2.Assess fish periodicity and habitat use by life stage (juvenile, adult and spawning) in the upstream, control, downstream, and project (diversion) reaches;
3.Determine juvenile fish densities and abundance within the different reaches of the project stream;
4.Determine adult fish abundance within the project and control reaches.
